"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-poland-intends-bid-2040-2044-summer-olympics-prime-minister-says\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"With the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris in the rearview mirror, at least one country has been inspired by the spectacle to pursue hosting its own Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999927720282097, \"rank\": 7.228024100131616e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Poland is readying a bid on the 2040 or 2044 Summer Olympics, prime minister Donald Tusk said in a Friday press conference.\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 156, \"end\": 162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9376001691520838, \"rank\": 0.06271597001073234, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}, {\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Tusk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Donald Tusk\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Tusk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Tusk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cLife will show whether this is a realistic goal.\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will take it seriously,\\\" Tusktoldreporters via Csongor Koromi of Politico.\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eastern European nation has bid on two past Olympics: the 2006 Winter Games that went to Turin, Italy and the 2022 Winter Games that went to Beijing.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/